Package com.qapel.rfid.entities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    QueuedTag
    Use this to capture information to be used for tags queued up for polling
    ReaderConfiguration
    Stations entity setup as a JBA entity for managing reader configuration in stations table
    Station
    Station entity for JBA model used to manage station identification in station table
    StationCache
    Cache station information that doesn't often change, so it can be looked up from information on tag without querying the database
    StationId
    Station Id entity used for generating unique ids for looking up station in cache
    StationReport
    Information to display in station report
    Tag
    Information related to a tag for internal processing and display
